# Repository Structure

Primary paths:
- `src/backend` — FastAPI + agent runtime
- `src/frontend` — React workshop UI
- `src/mcp-server` — MCP tools (spawned by backend)
- `sessions/` — released session packages
- `docs/` — operational documentation
- `config/` — local secrets (`config/.env`); template is root `.env.example`
- `tools/` — helper scripts (not runtime)
- `.github/` — rules, skills, agents, workflows, CI

Do not introduce references to non-existent or cross-repo directory trees in this repository.
